Events.Text: I need directions to hospitals from university by transit at 9am

Scenario.UserTask: You want directions from 'University' to 'Hospital' at 9 am by Transit. When the wizard gives the 2nd and 4th step, indicate that you do not understand until you are given more detail. Keep going until you've reached your destination.
Scenario.WizardTask: Tell the user the directions from their departure location to their arrival location
